Author: JoonieEra
Text: I don't think I have any kind of ointment for this. I have Vicks? I've never put that on a muscle strain before so I don't know if it works? I'm doing better today, I'm still in pain but I'm not freaking out anymore. I can walk now so im just gonna try to gently get some exercise. Thank you for caring and showing concern, it really means a lot to me that anyone even read this, it makes me feel validated.

Author: astankova
Text: Hey, I’m really sorry you’re going through this. Don’t panic. Don’t think about the calories. Do you have some ointment for your neck? Tiger Balm?
